<h2 style="color: #1A1A1A; margin-top: 0;">Rental Pickup Reminder</h2>

<p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>

<p>This is a friendly reminder that your rental pickup is coming up soon!</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><span class="label">Rental ID:</span> {{rentalId}}</p>
  {{#if rentalNumber}}
  <p><span class="label">Rental Number:</span> {{rentalNumber}}</p>
  {{/if}}
  <p><span class="label">Pickup Date:</span> {{pickupDate}}</p>
  {{#if pickupTime}}
  <p><span class="label">Pickup Time:</span> {{pickupTime}}</p>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if productName}}
  <p><span class="label">Item:</span> {{productName}}</p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

<p><strong>Please remember to bring:</strong></p>
<ul style="color: #555555;">
  <li>Your National ID (original)</li>
  <li>Any remaining balance payment (if applicable)</li>
</ul>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{storeUrl}}/account/rentals" class="btn-primary">View Rental Details</a>
</p>

<p>If you need to reschedule or have any questions, please contact us as soon as possible.</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br />
  <strong style="color: #D4AF37;">{{businessName}} Team</strong>
</p>
